---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
// V4 — NEGATIVE SPACE: Nothing/SpaceX minimal. Massive whitespace. One idea at a time.
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Catalyst Neuromorphic" description="Building neuromorphic processors to challenge the way intelligence is computed." hasFog={true}>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="v4-hero" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v4-center">
      <h1 class="v4-hero-heading reveal">AI has a hardware problem.</h1>
      <p class="v4-hero-sub reveal">We're building the processors to fix it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROBLEM 1 -->
  <section class="v4-scroll-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v4-center">
      <p class="v4-body reveal">Modern AI runs on hardware that was never designed for intelligence. GPUs burn hundreds of watts per chip. Data centres already consume over 2% of global electricity, and that share is climbing fast. Training a single large language model can use more energy than a hundred homes do in a year. The models are getting bigger, but the returns are shrinking.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROBLEM 2 -->
  <section class="v4-scroll-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v4-center">
      <p class="v4-body reveal">And for all that power, these systems still can't learn from new information without being retrained from scratch. They can't run without a data centre. They can't operate without sending your data to someone else's infrastructure.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROBLEM 3 -->
  <section class="v4-scroll-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v4-center">
      <p class="v4-body reveal">The human brain does all of this on 20 watts. It learns continuously. It processes information in real-time. It runs at the edge, on-device, with no internet connection required. The gap between biological intelligence and artificial intelligence isn't a software problem. It's a hardware problem.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE'RE BUILDING — heading -->
  <section class="v4-scroll-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v4-center">
      <h2 class="v4-section-heading reveal">Neuromorphic processors.</h2>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BUILDING 1 -->
  <section class="v4-scroll-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v4-center">
      <p class="v4-body reveal">Neuromorphic chips compute the way neurons do. They're event-driven &mdash; they only consume energy when there's something to process. They can learn on the hardware itself, not just run pre-trained models. They operate at the edge, on-device, without cloud dependency. And they do it at a fraction of the power cost.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BUILDING 2 -->
  <section class="v4-scroll-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v4-center">
      <p class="v4-body reveal">This technology exists. Intel has Loihi. IBM built TrueNorth. But both are closed, corporate, and inaccessible. If you're not inside those companies or their select research programmes, you don't get access. The hardware that could reshape computing is locked behind walls.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BUILDING 3 -->
  <section class="v4-scroll-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v4-center">
      <p class="v4-body reveal">Catalyst is building the open alternative. Full processor designs, published research, and a cloud platform anyone can use today. We're not asking for permission to compete with billion-dollar companies. We're just doing it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHERE WE ARE — heading -->
  <section class="v4-scroll-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v4-center">
      <h2 class="v4-section-heading reveal">Where we are.</h2>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATUS 1 -->
  <section class="v4-scroll-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v4-center">
      <p class="v4-body reveal">We're early. Two processor generations are designed, built in software, and validated on real hardware. Both have published papers you can read today. A cloud API is live &mdash; you can run a neuromorphic network right now, without buying anything.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATUS 2 -->
  <section class="v4-scroll-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v4-center">
      <p class="v4-body reveal">We're raising funding and building toward manufactured silicon. That's the goal: a physical chip you can hold, running real neuromorphic intelligence. We're not there yet. But the architecture is complete, tested, and protected by patent.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOUNDER -->
  <section class="v4-scroll-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v4-center">
      <p class="v4-founder reveal">Henry Shulayev Barnes</p>
      <p class="v4-founder-detail reveal">Engineering student at the University of Aberdeen. Started Catalyst because the neuromorphic hardware that should exist doesn't, and the hardware that does exist isn't accessible. Currently a member of Techscaler, Scotland's tech startup community.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TRUST ITEMS — each as a single line -->
  <section class="v4-scroll-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v4-center">
      <div class="v4-trust-list">
        <p class="v4-trust-item reveal">Read the papers. Two published papers on Zenodo with DOIs. Open access. Every claim documented.</p>
        <p class="v4-trust-item reveal">Try the cloud. The API is live. Run a neuromorphic network from your terminal. Free tier available.</p>
        <p class="v4-trust-item reveal">Check the hardware. Our designs run on real FPGA boards, not just simulators. Physical silicon execution.</p>
        <p class="v4-trust-item reveal">Join the community. Open GitHub, public research, growing backers. We build in the open.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IP -->
  <section class="v4-ip-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <div class="v4-center">
      <div class="v4-ip reveal">
        <p>UK Patents Filed Feb 2026</p>
        <p>RTL BSL 1.1 proprietary</p>
        <p>SDK BSL 1.1</p>
        <p>Papers open access Zenodo</p>
        <p>API Client MIT open source</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GET IN TOUCH -->
  <section class="connect-section" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-size:clamp(2.4rem,5vw,3.6rem); font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.035em; line-height:1.08; text-align:center; margin-bottom:18px;">Get in touch.</h2>
    <p class="connect-email"><a href="mailto:henry@catalyst-neuromorphic.com">henry@catalyst-neuromorphic.com</a></p>
    <div class="connect-grid">
      <a href="https://github.com/catalyst-neuromorphic" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="connect-card">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.4 5.4 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65S8.93 17.38 9 18v4"/><path d="M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2"/></svg>
        <span class="connect-label">GitHub</span>
        <span class="connect-sub">Source &amp; contributions</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/research" class="connect-card">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
        <span class="connect-label">Research</span>
        <span class="connect-sub">Papers &amp; benchmarks</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://ko-fi.com/catalystneuromorphic" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="connect-card">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
        <span class="connect-label">Support</span>
        <span class="connect-sub">Buy us a coffee on Ko-Fi</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style is:global>
    /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════
       V4 — NEGATIVE SPACE VARIANT
       Nothing / SpaceX minimalism. Massive breath.
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════ */

    /* Center container */
    .v4-center {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* Hero */
    .v4-hero {
      padding: clamp(160px, 25vh, 280px) 24px clamp(80px, 12vh, 140px);
    }
    .v4-hero-heading {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 8vw, 6rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      line-height: 1.05;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .v4-hero-sub {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
      margin-top: 24px;
      line-height: 2.0;
    }

    /* Scroll sections — massive vertical spacing */
    .v4-scroll-section {
      padding: clamp(120px, 20vh, 250px) 24px;
    }

    /* Body text */
    .v4-body {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      line-height: 2.0;
      text-align: left;
    }

    /* Section headings — lightweight */
    .v4-section-heading {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      line-height: 1.1;
      color: #fff;
    }

    /* Founder */
    .v4-founder {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .v4-founder-detail {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
      line-height: 2.0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* Trust items — single lines, no decoration */
    .v4-trust-list {
      text-align: left;
    }
    .v4-trust-item {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
      line-height: 2.0;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    }
    .v4-trust-item:first-child {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    }

    /* IP — tiny, understated */
    .v4-ip-section {
      padding: clamp(60px, 10vh, 120px) 24px clamp(40px, 6vh, 80px);
    }
    .v4-ip {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .v4-ip p {
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
      line-height: 2.4;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    /* ── Connect section ── */
    .connect-section { max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto; padding:80px 32px 100px; }
    .connect-email { font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-size:clamp(1.4rem,3vw,2.2rem); font-weight:600; letter-spacing:-0.02em; text-align:center; margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:56px; }
    .connect-email a { color:rgba(59,130,246,0.8); text-decoration:none; transition:color 0.3s; }
    .connect-email a:hover { color:#60A5FA; }
    .connect-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:20px; }
    .connect-card { display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; text-align:center; padding:36px 24px; border-radius:20px; text-decoration:none; color:#fff; background:linear-gradient(165deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.12) 0%,rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 35%,rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 100%); backdrop-filter:blur(28px) saturate(190%) brightness(1.06); -webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(28px) saturate(190%) brightness(1.06); border:1px solid transparent; box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.45),inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.14),inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.02); position:relative; overflow:hidden; transition:box-shadow 0.5s,transform 0.3s; }
    .connect-card:hover { transform:translateY(-3px); box-shadow:0 12px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.55),inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.18),inset 0 -1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }
    .connect-card::before { content:''; position:absolute; inset:0; border-radius:20px; padding:1px; background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(59,130,246,0.22) 0%,rgba(59,130,246,0.06) 25%,rgba(59,130,246,0.02) 50%,rgba(59,130,246,0.06) 75%,rgba(59,130,246,0.18) 100%); -webkit-mask:linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box,linear-gradient(#fff 0 0); -webkit-mask-composite:xor; mask-composite:exclude; pointer-events:none; z-index:5; opacity:0.55; transition:opacity 0.4s; }
    .connect-card:hover::before { opacity:1; }
    .connect-card svg { color:#60A5FA; margin-bottom:16px; position:relative; z-index:2; }
    .connect-label { font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif; font-size:1.05rem; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:6px; position:relative; z-index:2; }
    .connect-sub { font-size:0.78rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); position:relative; z-index:2; }
    @media(max-width:640px) { .connect-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; } }
  </style>

</BaseLayout>
